# apps/api (NestJS)

Read `docs/specs/api-outline.md` until `apps/api/openapi.json` exists — then treat OpenAPI as canonical.

## Boundaries

- Google SSO and session: `docs/specs/authentication.md`
- Credential vault + `/internal/*`: `docs/specs/credential-vault.md`
- No Playwright, no integration workflow execution in API
- LLM only in `ai` module; output must pass `libs/spec-kit` Zod schemas

## Swagger / OpenAPI

- Use `@nestjs/swagger` decorators on controllers and DTOs
- Dev UI: `/api/docs` (or `/docs` — pick one global prefix and document in README)
- Export spec in CI or via script → `apps/api/openapi.json` for agents

## Modules

`auth`, `users`, `credentials`, `tasks`, `chat`, `ai`, `queue`, `integrations`

## Env

Copy from `.env.example` — `CREDENTIAL_KEK` and `DATABASE_URL` only on API, never worker.
